---
title: Cheesy Smothered Mushroom Chicken with Roasted Carrots & Broccoli
description: Chicken and melted cheese is always a recipe for success. But chicken and melted cheese plus a rich gravy is the ultimate comfort trifecta. Here, chicken is topped with an umami-packed mushroom gravy and melty Monterey Jack cheese. On the side, there are creamy mashed potatoes and crispy roasted carrots for maximum deliciousness (and for catching any runaway gravy).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6256c3a98f1b9a3b357896ed-1d19611e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cheesy-smothered-mushroom-chicken-6256c3a98f1b9a3b357896ed-b247ffb4.pdf
